{"type": "article", "id": 11614, "title": "拿下尤文图斯新球衣，阿迪拍了一只怪瘆人的广告", "description": "嗳，谁对 EX 没点怨念呢？", "date": "2015-07-03T16:25:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9823, "name": "尤文图斯"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607135300mgvZPUTAwGDLNqlo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>为配合<span>尤文图斯 </span></span><span>2015 -16</span><span> 赛季球衣发布，阿迪达斯公布了短片 “</span><span>NO CLOWNS, JUST FOOTBALLERS. (</span><span>不是<span>小丑</span>，只是球员</span><span>)</span><span>”。尤文图斯当家球星博格巴、马尔基西奥等领衔主演。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTI3NTQwOTE2NA==\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>从视频内容看，阿迪达斯延续了此前 </span><span>#ThereWillBeHaters (</span><span>被嫉妒你够格吗</span><span>) <a href=\"http://huati.weibo.com/k/BeTheDifference?from=526\"><span>#BeTheDifference#</span></a> <a href=\"http://huati.weibo.com/k/%E5%BC%82%E7%B1%BB%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7?from=526\"><span>(</span></a></span><span>异类崛起</span><span>)</span><span>的一贯风格，再次采用了“没有小丑，唯有战士”的争议性话题，又是撕衣服，又是烧面具，也是让一众尤文球迷傻了眼，纷纷在阿迪达斯的官方微博下求科普自家球队和小丑的渊源。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135258jLdaNm329EToiFZt.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56338028\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2013</span><span> 年，意甲豪门尤文图斯与阿迪达斯达签下一份六年的合同，总金额为</span><span> 1.395</span><span> 亿欧元，此外还有额外的浮动奖金。<span>这意味着从</span><span> 2015 - 2016</span><span> 赛季开始，阿迪达斯将成为尤文图斯新的官方用品赞助商，取代此前合作长达</span><span> 12</span><span> 年的赞助商耐克公司。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135259PV3TifvcbQpYnmDG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><span><span> </span></span><span><em>2015 -16</em></span><span><em> 赛季尤文图斯客场球衣</em></span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t虽然早早地签下了合同，但是直到今年 6 月 30 号合约到期前，尤文图斯身穿着的依然是耐克战袍。而阿迪达斯此次发布的宣传语 “Our Way Or No Way” ，也可以显示出其对这位新宠儿十分上心。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}